                     <interp inst="t18511027-1951-offence-1" type="offenceSubcategory" value="simpleLarceny"></interp>, stealing 1 pair of trowsers, value 16<hi rend="italic">s</hi>.; the goods of <persName id="t18511027-name-740" type="victimName">
                        <interp inst="t18511027-name-740" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18511027-name-740" type="surname" value="FRANCIS"></interp>
